| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2806 — Recovery Inhibition (safepay)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cf7eaa2f-7cb6-5d29-a8b6-7616a62d6772"
